  <!-- WHY NYAYA-SETU -->
  <section class="ns-why">
    <div class="ns-why-inner">
      <div class="ns-why-header">
        <span class="ns-about-label">THE CHALLENGE</span>
        <h2 class="ns-about-sec-title">PROTECTING DIGITAL EVIDENCE</h2>
        <p class="ns-about-sec-desc">Digital files are fragile. They can be altered, lost, or faked. We solve this.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ns-why-grid">

        <div class="ns-why-card">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--danger">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title">Evidence Tampering</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">Digital files can easily be altered, swapped, or deleted before a trial. If a single file is changed, the entire case can fall apart.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-why-card">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--danger">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title">Lost Files & Failures</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">Traditional servers can fail or be hacked. When evidence is kept in just one place, an accident can permanently destroy critical information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-why-card">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--danger">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/>
              <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title">The Deepfake Threat</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">With modern AI tools, fabricating convincing video or audio is easier than ever. Courts need a guaranteed way to prove a file is 100% authentic.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-why-card ns-why-card--solution" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--gr">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="var(--e4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title ns-why-title--gr">Our Unbreakable Solution</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">By creating a unique "digital fingerprint" for every file and storing copies in 3 different systems (saving limits to Blockchain), we make it <em>impossible to secretly alter evidence</em>. Once it's in Nyaya-Setu, it stays authentic forever.</p>
          <a href="/evidence" class="ns-why-learn-more">
            View Live Evidence
            <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="ns-how">
    <div class="ns-how-inner">
      <div class="ns-how-header">
        <span class="ns-about-label">HOW IT WORKS</span>
        <h2 class="ns-about-sec-title">SIMPLE, SECURE, TRANSPARENT</h2>
        <p class="ns-about-sec-desc">From the crime scene to the courtroom, here is how we protect the truth.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ns-steps">

        <div class="ns-step">
          <div class="ns-step-num">01</div>
          <div class="ns-step-body">
            <div class="ns-step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="var(--c4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/>
                <polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/>
                <line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ns-step-title">UPLOAD</h3>
            <p class="ns-step-desc">Police upload digital files. The system instantly creates a unique digital fingerprint for each file.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-step-arrow">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,210,230,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-step">
          <div class="ns-step-num">02</div>
          <div class="ns-step-body">
            <div class="ns-step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="var(--c4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ns-step-title">SECURE</h3>
            <p class="ns-step-desc">Files are copied to 3 secure storage layers. The fingerprint is permanently locked using Blockchain.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-step-arrow">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,210,230,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-step">
          <div class="ns-step-num">03</div>
          <div class="ns-step-body">
            <div class="ns-step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="var(--e4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
                <path d="M21 12c0 4.97-4.03 9-9 9s-9-4.03-9-9 4.03-9 9-9 9 4.03 9 9z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ns-step-title">VERIFY</h3>
            <p class="ns-step-desc">Judges upload a file to verify. The system checks the fingerprint. A match means the file is 100% authentic.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div style="text-align:center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="ns-cta ns-cta--primary" style="display:inline-flex;">
          <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
          Go to Dashboard
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="ns-testi">
    <div class="ns-testi-inner">
      <div class="ns-how-header">
        <span class="ns-about-label">TESTIMONIALS</span>
        <h2 class="ns-about-sec-title">EMPOWERING THE JUSTICE SYSTEM</h2>
        <p class="ns-about-sec-desc">Hear how Nyaya-Setu makes life easier for everyone involved.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ns-testi-grid">

        <div class="ns-testi-card">
          <div class="ns-testi-quote">"</div>
          <p class="ns-testi-text">Before this, we spent weeks doing manual paperwork for every digital file. Now it's instantly secured the moment we upload. Our team can focus on investigating.</p>
          <div class="ns-testi-author">
            <div class="ns-testi-avatar ns-testi-avatar--c">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--c4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="ns-testi-name">Inspector R. Sharma</div>
              <div class="ns-testi-role">Cyber Crime Unit, Delhi Police</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-testi-card">
          <div class="ns-testi-quote">"</div>
          <p class="ns-testi-text">Checking if a file was original used to take months of lab work. Now I can verify it in under a minute right from my desk. It speeds up the whole trial process.</p>
          <div class="ns-testi-author">
            <div class="ns-testi-avatar ns-testi-avatar--g">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--e4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 6l9-4 9 4v6c0 5.25-3.75 10.15-9 11.5C6.75 22.15 3 17.25 3 12V6z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="ns-testi-name">Hon. Justice A. Mehta</div>
              <div class="ns-testi-role">Sessions Court, Mumbai</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-testi-card">
          <div class="ns-testi-quote">"</div>
          <p class="ns-testi-text">Our labs are always backed up with simple verification tasks. Nyaya-Setu handles the routine checks instantly, so we can finally focus on more complex cases.</p>
          <div class="ns-testi-author">
            <div class="ns-testi-avatar ns-testi-avatar--c">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--c4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.14M4.93 4.93a10 10 0 0 0 0 14.14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="ns-testi-name">Dr. P. Nair</div>
              <div class="ns-testi-role">Director, State Forensic Science Lab</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS BAR -->
  <section class="ns-threats">
    <div class="ns-threats-inner">
      <div class="ns-threat-card">
        <div class="ns-threat-val">0</div>
        <div class="ns-threat-lbl">Files Lost</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ns-threat-div"></div>
      <div class="ns-threat-card">
        <div class="ns-threat-val">100%</div>
        <div class="ns-threat-lbl">Tamper Proof</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ns-threat-div"></div>
      <div class="ns-threat-card">
        <div class="ns-threat-val">&lt; 1 min</div>
        <div class="ns-threat-lbl">Verification Time</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ns-threat-div"></div>
      <div class="ns-threat-card">
        <div class="ns-threat-val ns-threat-val--gr">3</div>
        <div class="ns-threat-lbl">Storage Layers</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<style>
